Yes to honesty and to growth!!  <br><br>
We could also add that if you are worried about your boy(girl)<br>
friend's temper, if you are frightened by it, if you are afraid<br>
to disagree, if you don't do or say things you want to<br>
because you are trying to avoid their anger, then watch out.<br><br>
This is not to say that all anger is bad.  Everybody gets angry<br>
We are allowed to get angry too!!<br>
Sometimes girls get the message that good girls are nice and<br>
never angry.  That is not true.  There are things to get angry <br>
about....<br><br>
But when anger is used to control or threaten other people, <br>
then it is a another clue to an unhealthy or dangerous <br>
relationship.<br><br>

